Journal
The Instituto Miguel As&lt;U+00ED&gt;n continues to publish the journal Al-Qantara. Revista de Estudios &lt;U+00C1&gt;rabes, in conjunction with the Consejo Superior de Investigaciones cient&lt;U+00ED&gt;ficas. Volume one of Al-Qantara [The Arch] was issued in 1980 at Madrid.
